# Copy file ini ke `.env` (sudah di-gitignore), lalu isi API key kamu.
# `.env` JANGAN di-commit — itu berisi credential.
#
# === OpenRouter (untuk AI narrative — gratis tier) ===
# Get API key: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# - Login dengan Google/GitHub account (no credit card needed untuk :free models)
# - Klik "Create Key" → copy ke baris di bawah
# - Model: openai/gpt-oss-120b:free — rate limited per minute, no daily token cap
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-openrouter-api-key-here

# === Anthropic Claude (opsional — alternatif paid) ===
# Get API key: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key-here
